Sit at the bar and have Brandon serve you.

created_at: you better hang on to it. Prices are affordable and service is stellar! They can get slammed so call ahead. Offers full service from waxes to lashes to your usual mani\/pedi. Impressed by the massaging chairs and cleanliness of spa. Best part

I also like the Lean & Mean omelette. Generous portions so I am the last person to vote for smaller portions. Is that really an issue for some? Pass it over to me then.

comment: I adore this unassuming spot. Parking is limited and tiny so wait can be long on weekends. I never have waffles unless it is here and it's the coconut waffle. OMG. This is golf heaven for anyone especially women. Only place I find large selection of actually fashionable golf outing wear but with a pretty penny. But is golf really a cheap sport? They have great staff ready to assist in your needs for drivers
author_id: balls and even lessons. It's like Legoland for adults. Or I am just a big kid :)

comment: The nori sliders are such a creative and filling choice. The crispy seaweed adds crunch to the ahi tuna. Presentation is eye catching. They are so good. Will have to venture back when I complete my meatless month challenge.

Service is impeccable. There is no bad seat in this restaurant. Have the rib eye with the wine sauce and sautéed mushrooms. OMG. I had a major orgasmic outburst. Talk to me with cow that's cooked perfectly medium rare with a side of wild mushrooms. Sold. And then top it off with the dessert. The chocolate tarte with the caramelized bananas seriously made love to my tastebuds.

comment: It's intimidating but makes you want to up your game. Why not? Who doesn't want to be fit and healthy! This is a gym for serious fitness people. Clean. Weights are well maintained. Great spot to watch the games bc the patio is open and tons of TV screens to delight your eyes. Taco Tuesdays is good for $2 tacos and $3 Dos XX. Get the carne asada
column5: and duck carnitas for sure. Generous with meat portions. Not on special but I love the street corn too! HH is 3-7 but tacos are the only deal along with beer. DO NOT order the Corona with Bacardi Limon and stick to the Dos!

comment: Try the sofritas. Tofu never tasted so good or spicy like this. And a great alternative to meatless Friday or if you want to be vegan which I'm not :)

author_id: delightfully blissful. This is an instant mood changer with the chai!

comment: Honestly Cartel. I am in love with you. Your staff. Your cappuccino. Your cowgirl cookie. You are utter happiness to me. I cannot get enough.
